{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886509728,"sessionID":"ses_284eae57bffeVf5e1aq0wThMJ0","part":{"id":"prt_d7b15a676001cmok1zFkB1U27Z","messageID":"msg_d7b157aab001ahWqkTD3jahYLL","sessionID":"ses_284eae57bffeVf5e1aq0wThMJ0","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_tool-3635c3d3a1b84107b69f4dadd82e7e0f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-034/CHANGE.md","newString":"## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-034\n- **Title**: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n- **Module**: .github\n- **Language**: YAML\n- **Size**: L\n- **Status**: Completed\n\n## Description\nCreate 12 GitHub Actions workflows for CI/CD pipeline automation in the AgentCube project.\n\n## Summary\n\n### Completed\nImplemented 12 comprehensive GitHub Actions workflows for CI/CD automation in the AgentCube project:\n\n1. **ci.yml** - Docker build verification on pull requests\n2. **lint.yml** - Go code linting with path filtering\n3. **codegen-check.yml** - Code generation drift detection\n4. **coverage.yml** - Race-enabled coverage tests\n5. **e2e.yml** - End-to-end testing on Kind cluster\n6. **python-sdk-tests.yml** - Python SDK unit tests\n7. **python-lint.yml** - Python code linting with Ruff\n8. **spelling.yml** - Spelling verification with codespell\n9. **copyright.yml** - Copyright header verification\n10. **release.yml** - Multi-architecture image publishing to GHCR\n11. **approve.yml** - Workflow approval for repeat contributors\n12. **dependencies.yml** - Periodic Go and Python dependency updates\n\nAll workflows include:\n- Proper trigger configurations\n- Path filtering where applicable\n- Concurrency control to cancel in-progress runs\n- Caching for Go modules and Python packages\n- Security best practices (pinned action versions, minimal permissions)\n- Appropriate timeout configurations\n- Artifact management (coverage reports, E2E logs on failure)\n\nComprehensive unit tests created in `tests/github/test_workflows.py` with 29/29 tests passing covering YAML syntax, triggers, path filtering, security, and more.\n\n### Deferred\nThe following items from the original task breakdown were deferred to future iterations:\n\n- **Deploy workflows**: `deploy-staging.yml` and `deploy-production.yml` (deployment automation)\n- **Documentation workflow**: `docs-build.yml` for automated documentation builds\n- **Security-scan workflow**: Dedicated `security-scan.yml` for comprehensive vulnerability scanning (Trivy, CodeQL, govulncheck)\n- **Reusable actions**: `.github/actions/` directory with shared action components\n- **Configuration files**: Dependabot, CODEOWNERS, PR/issue templates\n- **Workflow badges**: Status badges in README.md\n- **Branch protection**: Required workflow enforcement for main branch\n- **Notifications**: Slack/PagerDuty integration for workflow status\n- **Documentation**: Comprehensive GitHub Actions guide and maintenance guide\n\nThese deferred items represent advanced CI/CD features and documentation that can be added incrementally as the project matures.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\n- AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系 (workflows depend on Makefile targets)\n- AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (build workflow depends on Dockerfiles)","oldString":"## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-034\n- **Title**: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n- **Module**: .github\n- **Language**: YAML\n- **Size**: L\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nCreate 12 GitHub Actions workflows for CI/CD pipeline automation in the AgentCube project.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\nNone"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-034/CHANGE.md\n===================================================================\n--- /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T1